   
USAGE: toggle automail
   
This command arranges for NNGS to automatically send you all your
games by email, as soon as the games are completed. If you are already
receiving the games automatically, using this same command will make
the server stop the automatic mailings.
   
To see the current state of your automail and other such flags
that determine how your account acts on NNGS, type: variables
   
SEE ALSO: mail variables
   
